  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink204-kilavi"> varaiyātu vant* oḻukum talaimakaṉ ciṟa+ puṟattāṉ āka+ talaimakaḷ tōḻikku+
          colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the heroine told the confidante while the hero,
          who kept coming without marrying, was behind the hedge. </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink204">
          <l> aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉaiyaḵ tevaṉkol</l>
          <l> varaiyara makaḷiri ṉiraiyuṭaṉ kuḻīip</l>
          <l> peyarvuḻip peyarvuḻit tavirātu nōkki</l>
          <l> nalla ṇalla ḷeṉpa</l>
          <l> tīyēṉ ṟilla malaikiḻa vōṟkē</l>

        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
          <l>they say, </l>
          <l>having assembled in groups like mountain nymphs, </l>
          <l>looking relentlessly whenever [I] move, </l>
          <l>“she is good.” </l>

          <l rend="space">Why [then,] would it be that </l>
          <l> I am bad for the lord of the mountain? </l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
